	<entry>
		<title>Heaven Sent (Part 1)</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/58-the-luminous-mist/144-heaven-sent-part-1"/>
		<published>2015-06-09T19:00:19+00:00</published>
		<updated>2015-06-09T19:00:19+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/58-the-luminous-mist/144-heaven-sent-part-1</id>
		<author>
			<name>Kate Coady</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/121-gregg-marchese&quot;&gt;Gregg Marchese&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/nightmares-of-the-fall/144-heaven-sent-part-1&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/coady-beyond-the-green-luminous-mist-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A landscape with unexplained lights, glowing lava, old pahoehoe, a hint of an old straight road, low green auroras, and the beams of searchlights carried by two explorers.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;&quot;Many people went to the Halls of Honour and stood silently beholding the shrines and statues of the ancients, thinking of the enormous Second History of mankind since Night had prevailed upon the Earth.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/121-gregg-marchese&quot;&gt;Gregg Marchese&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
